# HTB - Dancing (Tier 0)
**Difficulty:** Very Easy
**OS:** Windows

## Tools Used
- nmap
- smbclient

## Steps
1. Connected Kali VM to HTB network via OpenVPN
2. Ran nmap -sV on target IP — found port 445 (SMB) open
3. Listed shares using `smbclient -L <IP> -N`
4. Found WorkShares accessible without password
5. Connected using `smbclient \\\\<IP>\\WorkShares -N`
6. Navigated directories, found flag.txt
7. Downloaded using `get flag.txt`, read with `cat flag.txt`

## What I Learned
- SMB shares misconfigured without authentication are common
- Always enumerate all shares, not just default ones
